      "content": "it's just not a matter of \"small steps\" anymore. it feels like there's no path back from this. the shame is so heavy, it's like it's part of my skin now. even if i fix the money, i can't un-fail them. i can't un-break their trust. sometimes it feels like the only way to actually stop the shame and the weight of everything is to just... exit. to just be done with it all so the disappointment stops being an option.",
